    src/kdatenav.cpp, src/kdated.h: add option to turn off hiliting
    of dates that simply have a daily recurring item on them in
    datenavigator; otherwise it starts to look really cluttered.
    Fixed kdatepicker in kdated so that if it loses focus it hides;
    we don't want it going "behind" the window it popped up over, this
    can get really confusing.

