1999-01-18  kulow  <kulow@xanadu>

    * /home/kde/kde-common/admin/automoc,
    /home/kde/kde-common/admin/ChangeLog: hey - another 140 lines diff
    for yet another cool option ;-)

    automoc understands now e.g. "META_INCLUDES = $(srcdir)/../include
    headers" for telling it where to look for header files. Please note
    that automoc only understands "$(srcdir)" in it, everything else would
    make things _way_ too complicated. But this is just for konsole ->
    since konsole works with it now, everything else has to work just
    fine ;-)

    (perl is like what my mother uses to call "es macht nicht schoen,
    aber es hilft!" ;-)

    * /home/kde/kde-common/admin/automoc: wrong error message

    * /home/kde/kde-common/admin/automoc: print out the correct filename
    when reporting errors

