1998-12-19  Preston Brown  <pbrown@xanadu>

    * src/topwidget.h, src/topwidget.cpp, src/kpropgroup.cpp,
    src/kagenda.cpp, src/calobject.h, src/calobject.cpp,
    src/alarmdaemon.cpp: changed all accelerators over to use KStdAccel.
    Man should have done that a long time ago.  Also, some more general
    cleanups.  Added method to the calendar to enable/disable dialogs.
    Kind of annoying when alarmdialog pops up error dialogs and you
    don't know really where they are coming from...

    * src/topwidget.h, src/topwidget.cpp, src/kontexthelp.h,
    src/kontexthelp.cpp, src/Makefile.am: removed 'kontexthelp', my
    failed attempt (from a long time ago) at a good context sensitive
    help system; kde/qt now has a better way, it is just a matter of
    using it.  Also modified Makefile.am so that unused code isn't getting
    compiled/linked in, thus reducing binary size/runtime footprint.

    * src/main.cpp: improved command line argument parsing to eliminate
    segfaults for bad ones, and also to be able to do 'korganizer
    filename' to give a new default calendar filename.

