1998-12-01  vespa  <vespa@xanadu>

    * src/kagenda.cpp: Added scrolling support when moving event widget.
    Boundaries work, dragging > 24:00 or < 00:00 is impossible now.
    Negavite times/sizes are also impossible.  Resizing past 24:00 stops
    at 23:59 Only resizing < 00:00 causes invalid time events.

    Only timer based scrolling is not in... ( for automatic multiple
    scrolling actions ) You have to generate a mouse event for each
    scrolling action (scrollbar step ).

1998-12-01  kulow  <kulow@xanadu>

    * /home/kde/kde-common/admin/acinclude.m4.in: a little bit more
    descriptive error message (also in config.log) and a way to override
    the test using $MOC

