    for events, allowing editing, deleting, etc. etc.  Also, you can use
    the regular menu entries to do the same, which you couldn't before.
    Man, the code is getting ugly though.  After the 1.0 release, I have
    to redo all the views (with lots of code reuse, but...) to inherit
    from one abstract view class.

