1998-11-15  Preston Brown  <pbrown@xanadu>

    * README: 0.9.17 version.

    * src/version.h, src/kagenda.cpp, korganizer.spec, korganizer.lsm,
    ChangeLog, BUGS: updates for 0.9.17.

    * po/pl.po, po/pl.gmo, po/no.po, po/no.gmo, po/korganizer.pot,
    po/fi.po, po/fi.gmo, po/de.po, po/de.gmo, po/Makefile.am: translations
    updated.

