    because so many are having crashes and problems.

    * src/holidays/holiday_portugal: holidays in portugal

    * src/holidays/Makefile.am, src/optionsdlg.cpp: holidays for
    portugal added.

    * src/kdpevent.cpp, src/eventwidget.cpp: widget summary handling
    worked on.

    * src/kdpevent.cpp, src/kagenda.cpp: calculation for # of recurrences
    now takes # of exceptions into account.

    * src/optionsdlg.cpp: extra time zone offsets added (for australia
    in particular).

    * src/eventwingeneral.cpp: fixed a bug ("TRUE" --> TRUE)

    * src/kagenda.h, src/kagenda.cpp: full monday week support added.

    * src/todoview.h, src/todoview.cpp: fonts support added.

    * src/kmonthview.cpp, src/kdated.h, src/kdated.cpp: font support
    added to monthview.  A few more QLineEdit --> QLabel fixes in kdated.

    * src/kdpevent.cpp, src/kdated.h, src/kdated.cpp: turned qlineedit
    into a qlabel in date editor (because editing in place is not
    implemented, and people were getting confused).  Fixed leapyear bugs
    in kdpevent.

