    files.

    * src/scanholiday.c, src/calobject.cpp: whoops!  parse_year takes
    a 2 digit (non y2k-ish) year, not a 4 digit year...so that's why
    ThanksGiving was on tuesday this year.  Fixed. :)

    * src/scanholiday.c, src/parseholiday.y, src/parseholiday.c: whoops --
    final fix to holiday parser.  I had the path stuff munged.

