    src/editeventwin.cpp, src/catdlg.cpp, src/calobject.cpp: Lots of
    things updated, oh my.  Bug fixes galore from all the e-mails I
    have received, especially segfaults in various places.  Spruced up
    the holiday support.  Complete overhaul of the online manual.
    Added "monday week support" i.e. there is an option so that the date
    navigator makes weeks start on monday instead of sunday.  Thanks to
    Roman Rohr for this code.

