    changes, the alarm daemon is smart enough to pick up the change.

    * src/topwidget.h, src/topwidget.cpp, src/optionsdlg.h,
    src/optionsdlg.cpp, src/kproptext.cpp, src/kpropfont.cpp,
    src/kpropdlg.h, src/kpropdlg.cpp, src/kpropcombo.cpp,
    src/kdpevent.cpp, src/calobject.h, src/calobject.cpp: automatically
    update owner of events if it changes in the config options.
    Fixed auto-updating of widgets after config options changed.

    * korganizer.spec: minor update to correct SPEC file.

    * Makefile.am: updates for minor 0.9.13 release.

    * korganizer.spec, korganizer.lsm, README: updates for korganizer
    0.9.13 (which will include the configure script!)

