    Vråle's norwegian translation.  Thanks a lot!

1998-09-17  Preston Brown  <pbrown@xanadu>

    * src/kdpevent.h: todos are created with an initial priority of 1,
    not 0.

    * src/topwidget.h, src/topwidget.cpp, src/ktimed.cpp,
    src/editeventwin.cpp: important changes that fix manual entry of
    times into ktimeds.

    * src/optionsdlg.cpp, src/ktimed.cpp, src/kagenda.h, src/kagenda.cpp,
    src/editeventwin.cpp, src/baselistview.cpp: work on configuration
    is proceeding.  We now support the new style 12/24 hour time option,
    an initial start time for appointments, and a "day begin hour",
    i.e. the first hour to display in Agenda View (instead of having it
    hardcoded to eight in the morning).

