1998-08-23  kulow  <kulow@xanadu>

    * acinclude.m4.in, /home/kde/kde-common/admin/acinclude.m4.in:
    added --enable-strict, which adds in case of gcc -W -ansi
    -pedantic -Wtraditional  -Wpointer-arith -Wcast-qual -Wcast-align
    -Wwrite-strings -Wconversion  -Woverloaded-virtual -Wundef
    -Wbad-function-cast  -Wsynth

    please be aware, that this makes code quite uncompilable :)

