    it was getting the week stuff all screwed up.  I'm tired.

1998-07-27  Preston Brown  <pbrown@xanadu>

    * src/kptbutton.cpp, src/editeventwin.h, src/editeventwin.cpp:
    started adding button for mailing event in the event editor window.

