    * src/kptbutton.cpp: hopefully fixed bug in kptbutton sizeHint where
    it was getting garbage from the text() method when none had been
    assigned to the button yet.

    * src/versit/Makefile.am, src/topwidget.cpp, korganizer.lsm, AUTHORS:
    small documentation additions and updates.

