    it out (I mean, flog it).

    * src/todoview.cpp, src/kptbutton.cpp, src/calobject.cpp: fixed
    sizeHint problem in KPTbutton, and some fixups on the todolist
    (fields getting filled in correctly now, working on due support).

    * src/kdatenav.cpp, src/kagenda.cpp: fix a stupid bug in kdatenav
    where selected date wasn't getting removed when moving around between
    months, and also a bug where the viewtype wasn't being auto-detected
    right in kagenda.

    * src/topwidget.h, src/topwidget.cpp, src/qdatelist.h, src/listview.h,
    src/listview.cpp, src/kmonthview.h, src/kmonthview.cpp,
    src/kdpevent.h, src/kdpevent.cpp, src/kdatenav.h, src/kdatenav.cpp,
