    src/calobject.cpp, src/baselistview.h, src/TODO: I switched all
    QList<QDate> to QDateList.  Hopefully all the memory problems that
    were caused by my stupid mistakes with dynamic allocation of dates
    and stuff like that is cleaned up by this.

