    * po/.cvsignore: more ignoring

    * src/topwidget.cpp, po/korganizer.pot: update

1998-04-27  cjbeard  <cjbeard@xanadu>

    * src/topwidget.cpp: doh! replaced '.cvs' with '.vcs' as default
    extension.

    * src/topwidget.cpp: Several things including bugfixes. The major
    change is behavioural and involves the use of default documents. Now,
    as I believe was intended, you can have a "New Calendar" which is
    unmodified. The application will now prompt you when you open it
    if you do not have a default calendar specified and I've rewritten
    the 'save', 'save as', 'close', and 'open' functions to do a little
    better job at sanity checking (you should no longer be able to open
    and close null files or directories), also i've added extension
    checking and appending as well as more error messages when things
    don't quite go right.

    * src/main.cpp: Removed the hack that I had put in place for the
    default document, and instead have it simply pass through as a new,
    unmodified calendar.

    * src/versit/Makefile.am: bugfixes, had to add rule for 'vcc.c' with
    proper dependencies and calling 'bison' to build it from 'vcc.y'
    grammar file.

    * src/Makefile.am: bugfixes, ordering of libraries for support of
    'versit' and 'libkab'.

1998-04-27  kulow  <kulow@xanadu>

    * src/topwidget.cpp, src/Makefile.am, po/korganizer.pot: merged
    some messages

    * src/versit/Makefile.am, po/korganizer.pot, src/kpbutton.cpp,
    po/Makefile.in, configure.in: added yacc support and made a message
    catalogue

