1997-12-28  kulow  <kulow@xanadu>

    * /home/kde/kde-common/admin/acinclude.m4.in: OK, kdebase configures
    now with the new path scheme. Let's see, how many problems the need
    of a DISPLAY makes ;)

    * /home/kde/kde-common/admin/acinclude.m4.in: extended my path
    scheme. The defaults (KFSSTND) are only hard coded within kdelibs,
    all other packages compile a little kapp and get the paths this
    way. I think, this is much more consistenter, since a change of
    KDEDIR between kdelibs and kdebase was very dangerous (even if not
    very probable ;)

