1997-11-03  kulow  <kulow@xanadu>

    * /home/kde/kde-common/admin/libtool.m4.in,
    /home/kde/kde-common/admin/acinclude.m4.in: changed the way,
    the compiler flags are set. I have copied some autoconf macros to
    acinclude.m4 and rewrote parts of them. Now it's possible to add more
    compilers and specify the right compilers flags (like -pto for CC).
    I thought about adding the flags (and compilers) of the QT Makefile
    to KDE and add a --with-gcc, but I think, this needs some kind of
    discussion ;)

