    the kcc Makefiles, I found, that the current Makefiles are not very
    clean. So I cleaned them up.  Note: It may be, that the one or the
    other app use now rpath. Please remove $KDEDIR/lib and $QTDIR/lib
    from your /etc/ld.so.conf and unset LD_..., so we can find this ones.
    I've removed the sentense about LD_... and KDEDIR from the toplevel
    Makefile

